
install wireshark on ubuntu:


bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ sudo apt-get install wireshark
bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ sudo wireshark 
bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ sudo groupadd  wireshark
groupadd: group 'wireshark' already exists
bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ sudo chgrp wireshark /usr/bin/dumpcap 
bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ sudo chmod 4755 /usr/bin/dumpcap 
bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ sudo gpasswd -a bwhite wireshark 
Adding user bwhite to group wireshark
bwhite@x:~/mygithub/known/linux$ 
